<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Facts:</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
1. A new Zek server is opening up. The ruleset is not yet determined.<br>
<br>
2. Faction hits are going away on ALL of the Zeks EXCEPT you will get a faction hit if you slay someone in their &quot;hometown&quot;.<br>
<br>
