<br>
Lady D has said that they aim to increase the population of the Zeks.<br>
<br>
Some ideas:<br>
Preventing PvP in the first 5 levels of a character's life.<br>
Free for all combat, anyone can hit anyone.<br>
They may get rid on Common Tongue as a language.<br>
<br>
Verified disappointments:<br>
Lady D said they can not do ANYTHING about fixing the LOS exploit where casters can cast through walls.<br>
<br>
Hopeful possibilities:<br>
Lady D wants to champion a move log option. And seems favorable to having one server locked down hardcoded teams and having another server be &quot;good vs evil&quot;. Deity based was also brought up.<br>
<br>
I'm sure I've forgotten some details so I will post if I remember more.<br>
